This release adds one of the most requested features to the Inkspace App content tagging to your library. You can now create your own tags for your content. Use your tags to sort search and organize all your notes in the Inkspace App and online on Inkspace Web.

This update significantly improves Inkspace performance and solves the most important issues reported by users. Content synchronization between platforms has been improved. Faster cloud synchronisation. Optimized transfer of content from smartpad to Wacom Inkspace app. Improved Ink to Text export functionality.

The Wacom Inkspace app is for your Intuos Pro Paper edition Bamboo Spark Folio and Slate. It replaces the Bamboo Spark app. Use the Wacom Inkspace app to turn what you write on paper into digital ink directly on your iOS device.
Bug fixes

New editing features for touching up your sketches or notes. Export as transparent PNG to take your ideas forward. Combine your notes on export and compile a multi page PDF. This update also provides a bug fix causing problems with exporting PDF s of your notes into email applications.
